MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BigShouldersInlineDisplay-Thin', Everything looks good.

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Big Shoulders Inline Display' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Thin' = NID 1 'Big Shoulders Inline Display Thin'.

Big Shoulders Inline Display Regular (BigShouldersInlineDisplay-Regular.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'BigShouldersInlineDisplay-Regular', Everything looks good.

Pass

Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. NID 6 is 'BigShouldersInlineDisplay-Bold', Everything looks good.

NID 6 is 'BigShouldersInlineDisplay-ExtraBold', Everything looks good.

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Big Shoulders Inline Display' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold' = NID 1 'Big Shoulders Inline Display ExtraBold'.
